'''寄蟎總目'''（{{lang|la|'''Parasitiformes'''}}），是[[蛛形綱|蛛形綱]][[蜱蟎亞綱|蜱蟎亞綱]]下的一個分類元。

本總目包含了所有[[蜱|蜱]][[蟎|蟎]]類的生物。這個總目的生物大多數都是[[寄生生物|寄生生物]]，但並非所有均是。舉例說：總目內約五千種屬於[[革蟎目|革蟎目]]的品種都是[[掠食性|掠食性]]生物，牠們[[隐居性动物|隐居]]在軟土、垃圾堆、腐木、糞便、腐肉、鳥巢或家居的塵埃裡。也有一些品種改以[[真菌|真菌]]、[[孢子|孢子]]或[[花粉|花粉]]作為食糧。[[植綏蟎|植綏蟎]]（[[捕植蟎科|捕植蟎科]]）在革蟎目佔約15％<ref>{{cite web |url=http://taibnet.sinica.edu.tw/chi/taibnet_species_list.php?D2=family&D3=equal&T1=Phytoseiidae&T1_new_value=false&query=Y&fr=y&sy=n |title=捕植蟎科 |accessdate=2016-01-19 |language=zh-hant |work=[[TaiBNET|TaiBNET]] |archive-date=2016-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126190113/http://taibnet.sinica.edu.tw/chi/taibnet_species_list.php?D2=family&D3=equal&T1=Phytoseiidae&T1_new_value=false&query=Y&fr=y&sy=n |dead-url=no }}</ref>，被用於[[生物控制|生物控制]]，並取得重大成就（見[[野草|野草]]條目）。

寄蟎總目實際上包含幾多品種，到現在還不清楚，因為有不少品種都是屬於隱居性動物，到現在還未有足夠的研究。據估量，現時世上所有寄蟎總目的生物大約有十萬到二十萬個品種，當中只有約1.2萬個品種是有文獻紀錄的。

==分類==
寄蟎總目最初只是一個亞目<ref>{{cite book |last=Schweizer |first=J. |year=1949 |title=Die Landmilben des schweizerischen Nationalparks: Teil 1 |trans_title=瑞士國家公園的蟎：第1部分 |language=de |location=[[利斯塔爾|Liestal]]: [[盧丁|Lüdin]] }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |first1=David |last1=Walter |first2=Heather |last2=Proctor |year=1999 |title=Mites: Ecology, Evolution and Behaviour |publisher=CABI Publishing |language=en }}</ref>。根據2004年的分類，本分類元為[[目_(生物)|目]]級<ref>{{cite journal |first1=S. C. |last1=BARKER |first2=A. |last2=MURRELL |year=2004 |title=Systematics and evolution of ticks with a list of valid genus and species names |journal=Parasitology |issue=129 |pages=S15-S36 |doi=10.1017/S0031182004005207 |language=en }}</ref><ref> Evolution of ticks Klompen, J S ; Black, W C ; Keirans, J E ; Oliver, J H Annual review of entomology, 1996, Vol.41, pp.141-61</ref><ref>John F Anderson, The natural history of ticks, Medical Clinics of North America, Volume 86, Issue 2, March 2002, Pages 205-218</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1055790306004052|pages=936–951|title=Phylogeny of parasitiform mites (Acari) based on rRNA|journal=Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution|volume=43|issue=3|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2006.10.024|author=Hans Klompen, Mariam Lekveishvili, William C. Black|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623170439/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1055790306004052|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年，寄蟎目升格成為現時的寄蟎總目<ref name="Krantz 2009">{{cite book |editors=Gerald W. Krantz, David E. Walter |title=A Manual of Acarology |edition=3rd edition |publisher=Texas Tech University Press |location=Lubbock, TX |year=2009| isbn=978-0-89672-620-8 |language=en }}</ref>，包括有下列四個目<ref name="Zootaxa_Parasitiformes">{{cite book |chapter=Superorder '''Parasitiformes''' <small>Reuter, 1909</small> |chapterurl=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2011/f/zt03148p128.pdf |format=[[可移植文档格式|可移植文档格式]] |authors=FRÉDÉRIC BEAULIEU, ASHLEY P.G. DOWLING, HANS KLOMPEN, GILBERTO J. DE MORAES & DAVID EVANS WALTER |url=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/list/2011/3148.html |title=Animal biodiversity: An outline of higher-level classification and survey of taxonomic richness |editor=Zhang, Z.-Q. |journal=[[Zootaxa|Zootaxa]] |issue=3148 |year=2011 |pages=123-128 |publisher=[[Magnolia_Press|Magnolia Press]] |isbn=978-1-86977-850-7 |issn=1175-5334 |language=en |access-date=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222175509/http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/list/2011/3148.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
* [[盲蛛目|盲蛛目]]（{{tsl|en|Opilioacarida||Opilioacarida}} <small>Zakhvatkin, 1952</small>，只有[[盲蛛總科|盲蛛總科]]一個總科，下轄34個現存種及兩個化石種）
* {{tsl|en|Holothyrida||Holothyrida}}目， Thon, 1905 (1个总科)
